from playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright
import time

with sync_playwright() as p:
    browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=False)
    page = browser.new_page()
    page.goto('https://www.google.com')
    # Googleの検索ボックスは'q'というname属性を持っています
    search_box = page.locator('textarea[name="q"]')
    search_box.fill('今日の天気')
    search_box.press('Enter')
    time.sleep(5) # 検索結果の表示を待つ
    browser.close()

import time

with sync_playwright() as p:
    # 9222ポートで起動している既存のブラウザに接続
    browser = p.chromium.connect_over_cdp("http://localhost:9222")
    # 既存の最初のタブ（ページ）を取得
    page = browser.contexts[0].pages[0]
    page.goto('https://www.google.com')
    search_box = page.locator('textarea[name="q"]')
    search_box.fill('playwright')
    search_box.press('Enter')
    time.sleep(5)
    # このケースではブラウザを閉じないのが一般的

import asyncio
from playwright.async_api import async_playwright

async def main():
    async with async_playwright() as p:
        browser = await p.chromium.launch(headless=False)
        page = await browser.new_page()
        await page.goto('https://www.google.com')
        search_box = page.locator('textarea[name="q"]')
        await search_box.fill('今日の天気')
        await search_box.press('Enter')
        await page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')
        # Keep browser open to see the result
        await page.pause()

if __name__ == '__main__':
    asyncio.run(main())

import pyautogui
import time
import pyperclip

time.sleep(1)

try:
    windows = gw.getWindowsWithTitle("メモ帳")
    if windows:
        window = windows[0]
        window.activate()
    else:
        subprocess.Popen(['notepad.exe'])
        time.sleep(1)
        windows = gw.getWindowsWithTitle("メモ帳")
        window = windows[0]
        window.activate()
except Exception as e:
    print(f"Error activating or launching Notepad: {e}")
    exit()

time.sleep(1)
pyperclip.copy("ABC")
pyautogui.hotkey('ctrl', 'v')
time.sleep(0.5)

    # Activate the first found window
    notepad_windows[0].activate()
    time.sleep(1)

    # Launch Notepad if no window is found

    time.sleep(2)

import asyncio
import nest_asyncio
from playwright.async_api import async_playwright

nest_asyncio.apply()

async def main():
    async with async_playwright() as p:
        browser = await p.chromium.launch(headless=False)
        page = await browser.new_page()
        await page.goto('https://www.google.com')
        search_box = page.locator('textarea[name=\"q\"]')
        await search_box.fill('今日の天気')
        await page.wait_for_timeout(1000) # Wait to avoid reCAPTCHA
        await search_box.press('Enter')
        await page.wait_for_load_state('networkidle')
        # Pause to keep the browser open
        await page.pause()

asyncio.run(main())
